[Logically the recent rains have flushed spores from a forgotten buried carcass up to the surface. This is a very flat part of Argentina so one cannot invoke downstream flushing.

To find Daireaux, go to http://www.fallingrain.com/world/AR/01/Daireaux.html. A HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map of Argentina can be seen at http://healthmap.org/r/9csf.

Our thanks to Ramon for this update. - Mod.MHJ]
